quran[15{c,v,t}:
19,96,yaqeenan jo log imaan le aeye hain aur amal Saleh kar rahay hain anqareeb Rehman unn ke liye dilon mein mohabbat peda kar day ga
19,97,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, iss kalaam ko hum ne aasaan kar ke tumhari zabaan mein isi liye nazil kya hai ke tum parhaiz gaaron ko khushkhabri day do aur hatt dharm logon ko dara do"
19,98,"un se pehlay hum kitni hi qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain, phir aaj kahin tum un ka nishaan paate ho ya unn ki bhanak bhi kahin sunai deti hai ?"
20,1,taah
20,2,hum ne yeh quran tum par is liye nazil nahi kya hai ke tum museebat mein par jao
20,3,yeh to aik yaad dehani hai har is shakhs ke liye jo daray
20,4,nazil kya gaya hai uss zaat ki taraf se jis ne peda kya hai zameen ko aur buland asmano ko
20,5,woh Rehman ( kaayenaat ke ) takhat saltanat par jalva farma hai
20,6,maalik hai unn sab cheezon ka jo asmano aur zameen mein hain aur jo zameen o aasman ke darmain mein hain aur jo matti ke neechay hain
20,7,"tum chahay apni baat pukaar kar kaho, woh to chupkay se kahi hui baat balkay is se makhfi tar baat bhi jaanta hai"
20,8,"woh Allah hai, is ke siwa koi khuda nahi, is ke liye behtareen naam hain"
20,9,aur tumhe kuch moose ki khabar bhi pohanchi hai ?
20,10,"jab ke is ne aik aag dekhi aur apne ghar walon se kaha ke"" zara tehro, mein ne aik aag dekhi hai, shayad ke tumahray liye aik aadh angara le aon, ya iss aag par mujhe ( rastay ke mutaliq ) koi rahnumai mil jaye """
20,11,"wahan pouncha to puraka gaya"" ae moose !"
20,12,"mein hi tera rab hon, jotiyan utaar day to waadi muqaddas tawee mein hai"
